disclaimer.title: Learn how reviews work
disclaimer.subtitle: Reviews from past guests help our community learn more about each home. By default, reviews are sorted by relevancy. Relevancy is based on recency, length, and information that you provide to us, such as your booking search, your country, and your language preferences. Only the guest who booked the reservation can leave a review, and Airbnb only moderates reviews flagged for not following our policies. To be eligible for a percentile ranking or guest favorite label, listings need 5 or more recent reviews. Criteria is subject to change. Learn more in our Help Center

htmlDescription.htmlText:
Forget your worries in this spacious, private space.

a separate new 1kk apartment in a quiet area of Prague 4, Budějovická metro. There is also a bus stop Hadovitá nearby.

The apartment has everything basic and necessary for a long and short stay of one or two guests.

I can send a video of the apartment to telegram @apart7prague

The space

reviews.comments: The apartment was clean and comfortable. It’s easy to get to the city centre using various transportation means. Also surrounding area is calm and communication with the host was easy and prompt.
Yana was very kind and extremely helpful, very quick to respond to any questions I had. An all-around great host.

The apartment is really convenient. There is everything one needs.
It is 10 minutes walking from actual station, from where there is direct team to the center of the city.
The host is extremely nice and helpful .
